flowchart LR

    Student[Student]

    subgraph Browser["Browser Client"]
        direction TB
        AppUI["App UI<br/>Chat, Study Mode, Dashboard"]
        ClientData["Client Data Layer<br/>Firestore listeners + mutations"]
        FnGateway["Functions Gateway<br/>SSE chat + study/focus calls"]
        FocusClient["Focus Engine<br/>remote inference + local fallback"]
        Collector["Data Collector<br/>/collect"]
        ZipExport[("Local Dataset ZIP<br/>download export")]

        AppUI --> ClientData
        AppUI --> FnGateway
        AppUI --> FocusClient
        ClientData --> FnGateway
        Collector --> ZipExport
    end

    subgraph Firebase["Firebase Platform"]
        direction TB
        Functions["Cloud Functions API"]
        Auth["Firebase Auth"]
        Firestore[("Firestore")]
        Storage[("Cloud Storage<br/>course materials")]
    end

    subgraph External["External / Adjacent Services"]
        direction TB
        Inference["FastAPI Inference Service<br/>separate runtime"]
        MediaPipe(["MediaPipe Assets<br/>WASM + face models"])
    end

    Student -->|main app flow| AppUI
    Student -->|data collection flow| Collector

    AppUI -->|sign-in / sign-up| Auth
    ClientData <-->|realtime reads/writes| Firestore
    ClientData -->|material upload| Storage
    FnGateway -->|HTTPS calls| Functions

    FocusClient -->|frame stream + summary| Inference
    FocusClient -.->|detector fallback| MediaPipe

    Collector -.->|calibration + labeling| MediaPipe

